---
title: Vanilla Cake
description: Delicious vanilla cake with classic flavor, perfect for any celebration.
---

Preheat oven to 350Â°F.

Cream @butter{1%cup} and @sugar{1.5%cup} together until light and fluffy, about 3 minutes.

Beat in @eggs{3} one at a time, then add @vanilla-extract{2%tsp} and mix well.

Combine @flour{2%cup}, @baking-powder{2%tsp}, and @salt{0.25%tsp} in a separate bowl.

Alternately add the flour mixture and @milk{0.5%cup} to the wet ingredients, starting and ending with the flour mixture.

Pour into a greased pan and bake for 30-35 minutes until a toothpick inserted in the center comes out clean.
